data.description: Priced to sell. This home has been owned since its construction in 2010 by a wonderful family that kept immaculate care of it. Wood floors in the living room will catch the attention of anyone who walks through the door. Perfect family home with top notch new schools very close by. With 4 bedrooms and a study there is room for any activity. This is a must see!!!
